sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Udvikler
    participant FE as Expo App
    participant BE as Convex Backend
    participant DB as Convex DB/Storage
    participant AU as Better Auth

    Dev->>Dev: Konfigurer .env.local
    Dev->>FE: npm install && npm run start
    Dev->>BE: Deploy Convex functions

    FE->>AU: Login/signup (email/password)
    AU->>BE: Session + auth claims
    BE->>DB: Gem/hent roller og profiler

    FE->>BE: Query/mutation (booking/admin)
    BE->>BE: AuthZ checks (role/salon access)
    BE->>DB: Læs/skriv booking, salon, staff, services
    DB-->>BE: Resultat
    BE-->>FE: Respons

    FE->>BE: createUploadUrl
    BE->>DB: Generer storage upload URL
    DB-->>FE: Upload URL

    Note over Dev,DB: Drift: monitorering, backup, versionsstyring og regelmæssig lint/test
